notification.communityContentToBeAnonymized: Ombinzi yose yo komunite yayo otaya kufihwa muhongomoka no kutailwa muufiku 7 sha kale, pombanda po otaya kushigeka okuyikuta kana okuyilongitha. Languluka ombinzi yawo okwa tale.

email.possibleFraudFooter: Kiliki okwa komunite linki okwa tale, kena ngaunona sha admin no ketha Fraud management oku menyu.
email.possibleFraudSubHeader: Omunyantantu wa omalungelo gokufumbolola okwa na omalungelo gokufumbolola 75% sha kale
email.possibleFraudInformation: Etokelelo lyetu lyokuzenzekelayo lyakutola omalungelo gokufumbolola. Onga languluka okuthika kwa komunite admin interface. Omahangu gokufumbolola ngoka ga ka kala na omayelelo gokufumbolola sha kale, noho kala oyelele okufufutala okulongitha ombinzi.
email.automaticToxicityDetection: Ombinzi ngoka otayi kufumbololwa okuzenzekelayo nga AI algorithms okukala otoxity ya ombinzi. Onga longitha ombinzi sha kale.
email.automaticToxicityDetectionVision: AI algorithm okuzenzekelayo otayi kufumbolola oshili shomifanekiso shokunangeshefa sha ombinzi ngoka. Algorithm ngoka otaala omifanekiso sha okukala omifanekiso ya omuntu omukulukumba, omulandu, omulwanyana, no omifanekiso yomukulukumba. Onga longitha ombinzi sha kale.
email.automaticToxicityDetectionDisclaimer: Kaholola ka AI algorithm o pima okukala okungalungi, omukalo gwawo shike, u na dhengifwa, o na kala oye na oshinyenyo shoka sha ningilwa, i ka na kala oye na oshitya oku email.
